mous
  pink and blue pearls that grow in the <span class=3DSpellE>Ucantium</span>
  clam, a shell-fish found deep in the seas of Ocean worlds.</p>
  <p class=3DMsoNormal>The <span class=3DSpellE>Ucantium</span> clam can li=
ve for
  thousands of years and can reach diameters of 5 meters or more. A single =
clam
  can produce hundreds of pearls.</p>
